law.text:
The court disposition level of the system shall consist of at least the following information as relates to counsel:
Did the defendant have counsel;
Did the defendant retain private counsel;
Was counsel provided by the public advocate;
If counsel was provided by the public advocate:
Was reimbursement sought;
What was the amount of reimbursement sought;
What was the amount of reimbursement paid; and
What amount was recovered from bail money;
Did the defendant have more than one (1) counsel; if so, the number of counsel.
